<p><span>报告期内，公司短期借款分别为</span><span>14.28</span><span>亿元、</span><span>26.42</span><span>亿元、</span><span>8.15</span><span>亿元、</span><span>4574.33</span><span>万元，一年内到期的非流动负债分别为</span><span>5.01</span><span>亿元、</span><span>6.03</span><span>亿元、</span><span>6.86</span><span>亿元、</span><span>7.60</span><span>亿元。</span></p>
