<p><span>截至当年末的逾期应收账款金额分别为</span><span>14.97</span><span>亿元、</span><span>17.08</span><span>亿元、</span><span>24.59</span><span>亿元、</span><span>28.21</span><span>亿元。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="123" src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201118/62870a02012f4f1c9c682afb1e7e584c.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>报告期内，公司应收票据金额分别为</span><span>10.43</span><span>亿元、</span><span>4.74</span><span>亿元、</span><span>10.34</span><span>亿元、</span><span>7.54</span><span>亿元，占流动资产的比例分别为</span><span>11.25%</span><span>、</span><span>4.53%</span><span>、</span><span>6.01%</span><span>、</span><span>2.24%</span><span>。</span></p>
