<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>此外，美的既是公司第一大客户又是第一大供应商。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份向前五大供应商采购金额占采购总额的比例分别为</span><span>76.58%</span><span>、</span><span>79.87%</span><span>、</span><span>70.39%</span><span>、</span><span>73.79%</span><span>。其中，向第一大供应商美的采购原材料占采购总额的比例分别为</span><span>66.03%</span><span>、</span><span>69.66%</span><span>、</span><span>60.66%</span><span>、</span><span>68.74%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>热交换器系列产品是销售收入中占比最高的产品，</span><span>2018</span><span>年销售单价较</span><span>2017</span><span>年下降</span><span>1.32%</span><span>，</span><span>2019</span><span>年销售单价较</span><span>2018</span><span>年下降</span><span>7.98%</span><span>。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，公司热交换器系列产品的销售收入分别为</span><span>5.51</span><span>亿元、</span><span>10.00</span><span>亿元、</span><span>11.79</span><span>亿元、</span><span>18.03</span><span>亿元，占主营业务收入的比例分别为</span><span>59.58%</span><span>、</span><span>66.85%</span><span>、</span><span>70.21%</span><span>、</span><span>70.56%</span><span>。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，热交换器系列产品平均单价分别为</span><span>234.27</span><span>元</span><span>/</span><span>套、</span><span>252.22</span><span>元</span><span>/</span><span>套、</span><span>248.89</span><span>元</span><span>/</span><span>套、</span><span>229.02</span><span>元</span><span>/</span><span>套。</span></p>
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>此外，德业股份线上销售渠道集中。德业股份表示，公司的环境电器系列产品采取线下线上同步发展的营销模式。在线上渠道方面，公司通过天猫商城、京东等电商平台，建立了线上直营和电商平台入仓的销售模式。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份线上销售渠道较为集中，通过天猫商城、京东合计实现销售收入</span><span>6729.73</span><span>万元、</span><span>7849.29</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.16</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.59</span><span>亿元，占线上销售收入的比例分别为</span><span>97.01%</span><span>、</span><span>98.45%</span><span>、</span><span>99.56%</span><span>、</span><span>99.29%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末，德业股份总资产分别为</span><span>6.11</span><span>亿元、</span><span>5.93</span><span>亿元、</span><span>8.68</span><span>亿元、</span><span>12.13</span><span>亿元，总负债分别为</span><span>3.53</span><span>亿元、</span><span>3.42</span><span>亿元、</span><span>5.41</span><span>亿元、</span><span>6.64</span><span>亿元，资产负债率（母公司）</span><span>62.33%</span><span>、</span><span>52.03%</span><span>、</span><span>56.43%</span><span>、</span><span>36.74%</span><span>，资产负债率（合并）分别为</span><span>57.81%</span><span>、</span><span>57.72%</span><span>、</span><span>62.27%</span><span>、</span><span>54.75%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末，德业股份总资产分别为</span><span>6.11</span><span>亿元、</span><span>5.93</span><span>亿元、</span><span>8.68</span><span>亿元、</span><span>12.13</span><span>亿元，总负债分别为</span><span>3.53</span><span>亿元、</span><span>3.42</span><span>亿元、</span><span>5.41</span><span>亿元、</span><span>6.64</span><span>亿元，资产负债率（母公司）</span><span>62.33%</span><span>、</span><span>52.03%</span><span>、</span><span>56.43%</span><span>、</span><span>36.74%</span><span>，资产负债率（合并）分别为</span><span>57.81%</span><span>、</span><span>57.72%</span><span>、</span><span>62.27%</span><span>、</span><span>54.75%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末、德业股份货币资金余额分别为</span><span>6568.81</span><span>万元、</span><span>8900.60</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.68</span><span>亿元、</span><span>4.38</span><span>亿元，占流动资产的比例分别为</span><span>15.98%</span><span>、</span><span>25.60%</span><span>、</span><span>28.57%</span><span>、</span><span>48.28%</span><span>。货币资金中，银行存款占比分别为</span><span>53.76%</span><span>、</span><span>58.07%</span><span>、</span><span>59.94%</span><span>、</span><span>84.74%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>公司的负债主要为流动负债，</span><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末，德业股份流动负债占负债总额的比例分别为</span><span>98.87%</span><span>、</span><span>99.11%</span><span>、</span><span>98.15%</span><span>、</span><span>98.06%</span><span>。公司的流动负债主要由短期借款、应付票据及应付账款构成，各期末，上述三项流动负债合计占报告期各期末流动负债的比例分别为</span><span>74.40%</span><span>、</span><span>85.45%</span><span>、</span><span>87.39%</span><span>、</span><span>84.59%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年，公司毛利率下降；</span><span>2019</span><span>年毛利率有所回升。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份主营业务毛利率分别为</span><span>24.68%</span><span>、</span><span>21.57%</span><span>、</span><span>19.28%</span><span>、</span><span>21.25%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>德业股份表示，公司不存在主营产品完全相同的同行业上市公司。公司与国内上市公司中主营产品相似企业的主营业务毛利率比较情况而言，</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，公司的主要产品热交换器系列产品毛利率分别为</span><span>23.23%</span><span>、</span><span>21.02%</span><span>、</span><span>17.49%</span><span>、</span><span>18.97%</span><span>，可比上市公司平均值分别为</span><span>28.12%</span><span>、</span><span>25.53%</span><span>、</span><span>22.56%</span><span>、</span><span>24.42%</span><span>。可以看出，可以看出，德业股份热交换器系列产品毛利率与同行业水平存在一定差异。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末，德业股份应收账款总额分别为</span><span>5044.27</span><span>万元、</span><span>7460.68</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.63</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.64</span><span>亿元，占当期营业收入比例分别为</span><span>5.42%</span><span>、</span><span>4.95%</span><span>、</span><span>9.63%</span><span>、</span><span>10.25%</span><span>。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份应收账款周转率（次）分别为</span><span>20.33</span><span>、</span><span>24.09</span><span>、</span><span>14.25</span><span>、</span><span>12.06</span><span>，同行业可比上市公司应收账款周转率平均值（次）分别为</span><span>12.77</span><span>、</span><span>13.84</span><span>、</span><span>13.01</span><span>、</span><span>8.34</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末，德业股份存货余额分别为</span><span>1.43</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.58</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.02</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.99</span><span>亿元，由原材料、在产品、库存商品和发出商品构成，其中原材料和库存商品合计占存货余额的比例分别为</span><span>85.45%</span><span>、</span><span>76.69%</span><span>、</span><span>82.96%</span><span>、</span><span>70.84%</span><span>。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份存货周转率（次）</span><span>6.08</span><span>、</span><span>7.86</span><span>、</span><span>7.59</span><span>、</span><span>10.12</span><span>，同行业可比上市公司存货周转率平均值分别为（次）</span><span>5.45</span><span>、</span><span>5.72</span><span>、</span><span>5.41</span><span>、</span><span>4.41</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2019</span><span>年公司研发费用占营业收入比例下降。</span><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份研发费用分别为</span><span>3079.54</span><span>万元、</span><span>5692.90</span><span>万元、</span><span>7026.22</span><span>万元、</span><span>8679.55</span><span>万元，研发费用占营业收入比例分别为</span><span>3.31%</span><span>、</span><span>3.78%</span><span>、</span><span>4.16%</span><span>、</span><span>3.38%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年，德业股份存在关联方资金拆借情况。</span><span>2016</span><span>年，德业股份实际控制人及其关联方共拆出资金</span><span>2.53</span><span>亿元，共拆入资金</span><span>7910</span><span>万元。</span><span>2017</span><span>年，德业股份实际控制人及其关联方共拆出资金</span><span>2869.82</span><span>万元，共拆入资金</span><span>1445</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>德业股份的全资子公司德业变频曾挂牌新三板。</span><span>2015</span><span>年</span><span>5</span><span>月</span><span>29</span><span>日，德业变频在全国股转系统挂牌公开转让，证券代码为“</span><span>832525</span><span>”。自</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>11</span><span>月</span><span>24</span><span>日起，德业变频终止在全国股转系统挂牌。</span></p>
<p><span>德业变频与关联企业发生非经营性资金占用，被出具警示函，违规占用资金近</span><span>9000</span><span>万元。德业变频于</span><span>2016</span><span>年</span><span>9</span><span>月</span><span>5</span><span>日收到宁波市证监局出具的《行政监管措施决定书》，认为德业股份子公司德业变频自</span><span>2015</span><span>年初至</span><span>2015</span><span>年</span><span>5</span><span>月</span><span>29</span><span>日在股转系统挂牌期间，与关联公司发生非经营性资金占用共计</span><span>3800</span><span>万元，余额</span><span>3240</span><span>万元；德业变频自挂牌日起至</span><span>2015</span><span>年</span><span>8</span><span>月</span><span>10</span><span>日，与关联企业德业有限发生</span><span>3</span><span>次非经营性资金占用共计</span><span>3557.25</span><span>万元，自挂牌日起至</span><span>2015</span><span>年</span><span>7</span><span>月</span><span>4</span><span>日，与关联企业德威福尔发生</span><span>3</span><span>次非经营性资金占用共计</span><span>1400</span><span>万元。上述行为违反了《非上市公众公司监督管理办法》第十三条、第十四条和第二十条的规定，根据《非上市公众公司监督管理办法》第五十六条规定，对德业变频采取出具警示函的行政监管措施。</span></p>
<p><span>报告期内，德业股份存在废料收入通过实际控制人之妻陆亚珠、实际控制人之子张栋斌个人卡，零星货款通过实际控制人之子张栋业个人卡收款的情况。</span><span>2017</span><span>年，通过个人银行卡收款金额合计</span><span>726.97</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>对比环评文件和招股书，公司募投项目建设期存在两年的时间出入，采购的生产设备数量不一致。据壹财信，对于除补充流动资金之外的其他四个项目的建设期，德业股份招股书显示分别计划用</span><span>1</span><span>年、</span><span>1</span><span>年、</span><span>1</span><span>年、</span><span>18</span><span>个月的时间完成建设，完成建设后开始投产。然而环评文件显示，上述四个项目的计划开工时间均为</span><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>11</span><span>月，预计投产时间均为</span><span>2022</span><span>年</span><span>10</span><span>月，项目建设周期均为</span><span>36</span><span>个月。此外，四个募投项目采购的生产设备数量与环评文件中也存在数量不一致。</span></p>
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>德业股份回复中国经济网，招股书显示四个项目分别计划用</span><span>1</span><span>年、</span><span>1</span><span>年、</span><span>1</span><span>年、</span><span>18</span><span>个月的时间完成建设，该时间为预计的实际建设时间，环评文件显示项目建设周期均为</span><span>36</span><span>个月，该时间为根据土地出让合同规定的最长建设时间。招股书显示四个募投项目采购的生产设备数量与环评文件中也存在数量不一致的情况，原因为两个数量均为挑选的主要设备，选取的口径存在差异导致。</span></p>
<p><strong><span>3</span><span>年多分红</span><span>2.97</span><span>亿元</span><span>拟募资</span><span>10</span><span>亿</span></strong></p>
<p><span>德业股份主要从事蒸发器、冷凝器和变频控制芯片等部件以及除湿机和空气源热泵热风机等环境电器产品的研发、生产和销售。</span></p>
<p><span>艾思睿投资持有公司</span><span>6480.64</span><span>万股，持股比例为</span><span>50.63%</span><span>，为公司的控股股东。张和君直接持有公司</span><span>32.00%</span><span>的股份，通过持有控股股东艾思睿投资</span><span>99.00%</span><span>的股权而间接控制发行人</span><span>50.63%</span><span>的股份，通过担任亨丽投资的普通合伙人及执行事务合伙人而间接控制公司</span><span>3.37%</span><span>的股份。张和君通过直接及间接方式合计控制公司</span><span>86.00%</span><span>的股份，为公司的实际控制人。</span></p>
<p><span>德业股份拟在上交所主板上市，发行股数</span><span>4266.70</span><span>万股，保荐机构为光大证券。德业股份拟募集资金</span><span>10.21</span><span>亿元，其中，</span><span>1.86</span><span>亿元用于年产</span><span>150</span><span>万套热交换器系列产品生产线建设项目，</span><span>3.71</span><span>亿元用于年产</span><span>55</span><span>万台环境电器系列产品生产线建设项目，</span><span>1.86</span><span>亿元用于年产</span><span>74.9</span><span>万套电路控制系列产品生产线建设项目，</span><span>7711.63</span><span>万元用于研发中心建设项目，</span><span>2</span><span>亿元用于补充流动资金项目。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="402" src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201118/d1b57d5448a04b7fb7942758c409cb93.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>关于公司股利分配情况，</span><span>2016</span><span>年</span><span>12</span><span>月</span><span>-2020</span><span>年</span><span>3</span><span>月，德业股份</span><span>3</span><span>年多累计分红</span><span>2.97</span><span>亿元。</span></p>
<p><span>德业股份招股书显示，根据</span><span>2016</span><span>年</span><span>12</span><span>月召开股东决定，分配现金股利</span><span>1.05</span><span>亿元；根据</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月召开股东会决议，分配现金股利</span><span>5000</span><span>万元；根据</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>9</span><span>月召开股东会决议，分配现金股利</span><span>4000</span><span>万元；根据</span><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>5</span><span>月召开股东大会决议，分配现金股利</span><span>3840</span><span>万元。根据</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>3</span><span>月召开股东大会决议，分配现金股利</span><span>6400</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><strong><span>4</span><span>年收到现金不及营收</span></strong></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份实现营业收入分别为</span><span>9.30</span><span>亿元、</span><span>15.06</span><span>亿元、</span><span>16.91</span><span>亿元、</span><span>25.70</span><span>亿元，主营业务收入分别为</span><span>9.25</span><span>亿元、</span><span>14.96</span><span>亿元、</span><span>16.80</span><span>亿元、</span><span>25.55</span><span>亿元，销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金分别为</span><span>4.33</span><span>亿元、</span><span>6.00</span><span>亿元、</span><span>7.73</span><span>亿元、</span><span>12.33</span><span>亿元。同期，德业股份主营业务收现比率（销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金</span><span>/</span><span>主营业务收入）分别为</span><span>46.77%</span><span>、</span><span>40.10%</span><span>、</span><span>45.99%</span><span>、</span><span>48.26%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，德业股份实现归属于母公司股东的净利润分别为</span><span>9052.86</span><span>万元、</span><span>9302.28</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.02</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.60</span><span>亿元，扣除非经常性损益后的归属于公司普通股股东的净利润分别为</span><span>8417.72</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.30</span><span>亿元、</span><span>9694.67</span><span>万元、</span><span>2.43</span><span>亿元，经营活动产生的现金流量净额分别为</span><span>1.42</span><span>亿元、</span><span>7682.62</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.66</span><span>亿元、</span><span>3.81</span><span>亿元。</span></p>
